  "title": "Accounting Executive / Accountant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> CT Hub, 2 Kallang Avenue, Singapore 339407</p><p><strong>About Us:</strong><br />\nWe are a professional accounting firm dedicated to providing high-quality\nservices to our clients. We foster a collaborative and supportive work\nenvironment and strongly promote work–life balance.<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Bookkeeping transactions for partial or full sets of multiple clients’ accounts.</li><li>Prepare management accounts and director statements for year-end filing.</li><li>Prepare quarterly GST returns.</li><li>Prepare tax computations and Form C/CS for company income tax.</li><li>Perform other filings, e.g., IR21, IR8A, GST registration.</li><li>Perform ACRA filings.</li><li>Perform any other duties as required.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum qualification: LCCI/Diploma in Accounting or equivalent.</li><li>At least 3 years of relevant working experience.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office applications (Word & Excel).</li><li>Strong sense of responsibility, maturity, self-initiative, proactivity, attention to detail, good interpersonal skills, and ability to work independently.</li><li>Bilingual proficiency in English and Mandarin to effectively communicate with clients of different language backgrounds.</li></ul><ul><li>Working Days: Monday to Friday</li></ul>",
