    "description": "<p> <br />\nAZ Bizcorp Management Pte Ltd is an integrated professional services firm offering accounting, tax, compliance, statutory secretary and other compliance services.<br />\nOur team are comprised by members of Chartered Accountants (CA Singapore), the Association of Chartered Certified Accountants (ACCA), Accredited Tax Practitioner (Income Tax & GST) of the Singapore Institute of Accredited Tax Professionals (SIATP) with about 20 years’ experience in audit firms, commercial firms, Singapore and overseas listed companies.<br />\nWe are also the Registered Filing Agent with the Accounting and Corporate Regulatory Authority of Singapore (ACRA), which enables us to facilitate Company incorporations, and compliance filing services.<br />\nWe believe that our industry knowledge and understanding of local and overseas business dynamics that made us the team to be reckoned with. It is our mission to establish long term partnership and to grow with our clients.<br />\n <br />\n </p>\n",
